This package installs laymans and any required overlays.

@author Gunnar Wrobel <p@rdus.de>
@version 1.0
@package tool_layman

@module os_gentoo     The os_gentoo module is required for Gentoo support.

@fact operatingsystem Allows to choose the correct actions depending
                      on the operating system

@param portage_layman_storage       The path to layman overlays (Default:
                                    '/usr/local/portage/layman')
@param portage_layman_remote_lists  A comma separated list of paths to any
                                    additional overlay lists that you want to
                                    make accessible to layman. (Default: '')
@param portage_layman_overlays      A comma separated list of overlays you want
                                    to install in the system.
